quizzes.textContent:
[h1]If Else[/h1]

The example below will output the greatest number of the two.[code format="php" codeId="476"]<?php
$x = 10;
$y = 20;
[b]if [/b]([b]$x >= $y[/b]) {
   echo $x;
} [b]else [/b]{
   echo $y;
}

// Outputs "20"
?>[/code]
